Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister! We want to go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about it?! If you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "sky island"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But the Log Pose is\Ndefinitely pointing to the sky!\N--Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm just taking him up on his offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro! Forget the promise,\Ntake care of them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take them on, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Distinguished Pirates! A Man Who Talks of\NDreams and the King of Undersea Search"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them! They're still standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get those clumsy chickens!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town isn't for dreaming cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the Bellamy Pirates\Nare holding a public lynching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro! Why are you\Njust taking this from them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight them! Why don't you just beat them up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, lady. They're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've realized that their\Nopponents are out of their league.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not fighting a strong opponent...\Nit's a disgraceful move, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he has no dignity as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's generous these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,giving 30 million Berries for the\Nhead of a worthless ass like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, don't take them on,\Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... are you both...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctrine of nonresistance...\NSounds nice, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to being weak, you have no pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get into a single fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your head is full of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A weak-looking shorty worth 30 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what kind of man he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just a letdown, it's boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met cowards like them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get them out of my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're eyesores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to move forward\Ninto the new era if you're with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I buy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it cost to have you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? You're going to buy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Join us. It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm too good for a team\Nof small fries like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their gang is nothing but dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take those two and beat it already
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you're still alive, you small fries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't ever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky island exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry pies here really are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so angry, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who won the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You'll surpass us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again when we\Nbecome distinguished pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sharp retort was really something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new era they're talking about is crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The era where pirates have dreams\Nwill be over, they say?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People's dreams... have no end!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you suddenly shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about people's dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outdoing others isn't easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has your brain melted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? I hear a ruckus outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. Those guys might be goin'\Non a rampage 'cause they're pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can go ahead and laugh at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you aim high, you sometimes\Ncome across fights not worth fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like I interrupted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he might've known\Nsomething about the sky island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... And it's not "he."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's not "he"? Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"They," probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean there were\Nothers with him? Where?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drinks sure taste good today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Panel!\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nail!\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Panel!\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... I know I'm repeating myself,\Nbut I'm not a shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're really handy with stuff, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I?! That's the amazing thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just buy a new ship instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts?! Do you know\Nhow we got this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I've heard it so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was given to you guys by a\Npretty girl from your village, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, it's dangerous to keep\Ntraveling on a ship in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm repairing it!\NGive us a hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repair? You call this repair?\NYou're just patching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a funny face, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... About tonight's dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, so you don't want any?\N--Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahhh! We do!!\N--Now, I wonder how the seagull\Nstock soup is coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We do!! Sanji-kun!!\N--Now, I wonder how the seagull\Nstock soup is coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please let us eat!!\N--Now, I wonder how the seagull\Nstock soup is coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salvage, salvage...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Salvage, salvage...\N--Wh-What's with that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Salvage...\N--This song is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-L-L-Luffy! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wounded?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D-Doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So check them out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of Moguera\Nmonster did you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates. But that's okay, it's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's over for you guys,\Nit's not over for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?! You're men, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone provokes you, you should\Njust go ahead and beat them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, better yet, why not just\Nblow up this whole annoying town!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what was that stuff you said earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's past is past!\NDon't talk about ancient history!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to floor you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's she in such a mood\Nabout when she's unhurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Did you get any\Ninformation about the sky island?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky... island...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! All I did was mention "sky island,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the entire bar broke out laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ketchup Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite lively up there.\NWhy are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Welcome back, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to eat first,\Nor shall I prepare your bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Robin, did you go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I got some clothes and\Ninformation about the sky island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You, Robin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Jumping Point!\N--This all happened because you\Nstarted talking about that sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Chopper!\N--I'll send you to a watery grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, leave her alone for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, you'd better not get\Nclose to her. Just don't rock the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's a treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Isn't it just an ordinary map? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town drawn on the left is\NMock Town, where we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see an x on the other side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that a man who doesn't\Nblend in in Jaya lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't blend in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Montblanc Cricket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who talked about dreams\Nand was driven out of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have something\Nin common to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't we try going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec, Luffy. I'm not sure\Nif we should go now because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper, you saw it\Nearlier, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nami was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tryin' to say I'm some\Nsimple-minded idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big boss! Undersea preparations complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mic's ready, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Starting the search sonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Utan Diver Number 27!\NSonar response confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School of fish detected at 9 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From it's swimming speed,\Nwe've determined that it's saury.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We'll have them\Nroasted whole for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Diver Number 4!\NSonar response confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small sailing vessel\Ndetected traveling on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A vessel?\NDetermine the exact direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I'd say it's at 12 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already close enough to see!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the search and return\Nto the ship, Utan Divers!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't take long for us to\Ncome across something weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't look like the\Nsame guys from before, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whether that's a good thing\Nor a bad thing is another story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we did see them! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As we thought,\Nthat salvager is from this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw his ship coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... but I don't mind seeing him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, you guys! Quit mumbling over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Honestly, I got all worked up\Nwondering who you guys were!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a reckless face\Nyou've got! What species are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm human, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You punks! Don't you know Shojo-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the big boss of the Shojo Pirates\Nand the king of undersea search!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make our big boss angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that Crocodile, one of the\NSeven Warlords of the Sea, was defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you consider my abilities,\Nthat post may come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been getting all worked\Nup waiting to be contacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then you want to become one\Nof the Seven Warlords of the Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in any case, the great part about me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that I haven't had my hair\Ncut in all my 25 years of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, aren't you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... What you say\Nreally gets me all worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. You will come out of the tunnel\Nthat is my anger into a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, whatever...\Nbut there's a place we wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! This area is my turf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna pass through, pay the toll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he mean by his turf?\NHe's talking like Masira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did Masira say stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Masira?! What about Masira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kicked him off our boat, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kicked... Kicked...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big boss!\N--Kicked?! How dare you do that to my brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is revenge for Masira!\N--Hey, hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kicked him, but he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Havoc Sonar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So... what're they doing?\N--Big boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who knows? But it's amazing.\N--If you use that technique on the ship, it'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's destroying their ship with his voice.\N--Oh, no! He's blinded by anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone! Stop gawking and\Nlet's get through here while we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami's not a demon any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she should be calmer\Nafter letting off that much steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! The waves\Nmade it to this ship after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's starting to fall apart,\Nparticularly the repaired areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's body is worn out enough as it is!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here, the ship will be torn apart!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead! To someplace\Nout of his voice's reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this pretty woman says,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tell me where this Cricket lives!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bold woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bold? Well, she was strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had these mysterious hands\Npopping out everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they knocked down everyone\Nin the bar. It wasn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does she want\Nwith old geezer Cricket?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea around there is the turf\Nof the big monkey brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you have something\Nto do with that old geezer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll catch his stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What that woman's after is\Ngold bullion, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gold bullion?!\N--Yeah. I heard some gold\Nbullion was found recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say about gold bullion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Cricket guy...\NI'd definitely like to meet him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me all about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:22:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:23:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is, uh... what's his name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Montblanc Cricket.\N--This is his house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a picture book!\NIt's titled "Noland the Liar"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's a cool name!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that brings back memories.\NI read it a lot when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you know it?\N--Yeah. I heard that he was a real person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Legendary Family! 'Noland the Liar'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
